content.content: Alice ask me to visit www.resume_templates.com to download the resume template we will use. Please help me to download the file and save it to /documents.

conversations.content:
<|Function_Thought|>
Since the user asked to visit a specific URL to download a template, the appropriate step would be to browse the webpage first and then proceed to download the file directly from that URL. I will initiate browsing the provided URL.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Function_Call|>[browse_webpage(url="www.resume_templates.com")]<|/Function_Call|>

content.content:
